01:29:46,172 --> 01:29:47,173
Green.

1129
01:29:50,135 --> 01:29:51,136
Blue.

1130
01:29:55,473 --> 01:29:56,474
Pink.

1131
01:30:02,814 --> 01:30:03,815
Black.

1132
01:30:08,987 --> 01:30:09,988
Red.

