1261
01:40:39,951 --> 01:40:40,952
"Who are we?

1262
01:40:42,578 --> 01:40:43,704
"Why are we here?

1263
01:40:44,288 --> 01:40:45,540
"If we ever learn this,

1264
01:40:45,623 --> 01:40:48,217
